content:
Improve phone support with Service Cloud Voice. Service Cloud Voice is completely integrated into Salesforce, providing a consistent experience for agents, supervisors, and customers across all digital channels.

Service Cloud Voice offers these unique benefits:

* Architecture: A scalable, resilient architecture designed for high-volume contact centers.
* AI: Integrated with Einstein, providing Conversation Intelligence features and automating common tasks.
* Supervisor experience: Integrated with Omni Supervisor, offering a unified view of agents' calls and conversations.
* Agent experience: Leveraging the Omni-Channel widget, enabling agents to transfer customers between channels and gather context across those channels.
* Customer experience: Enabling proactive and personalized service through Omni-Channel flows.

Service Cloud Voice supports multiple telephony systems and integrates with Einstein for Conversation Intelligence features. It also allows supervisors to view agent calls and conversations, and enables agents to transfer customers between channels while gathering context.

Service Cloud Voice is available in Lightning Experience, Enterprise and Unlimited Editions, Sales Cloud, Service Cloud, and Government Cloud as an add-on license.

Use Service Cloud Voice Across Sales and Service by leveraging its features in both service and sales operations.
title: Service Cloud Voice
